<p><img width="2997" height="4000" src="https://news.tokunation.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2023/10/new-garo.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://news.tokunation.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2023/10/new-garo.jpg 2997w, https://news.tokunation.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2023/10/new-garo-112x150.jpg 112w" sizes="(max-width: 2997px) 100vw, 2997px" /></p><p>Fans of <strong>Garo</strong> rejoice &#8211; after years of nothing, a brand new <strong>Garo</strong> series has been announced!  <strong>Garo &#8211; The One Who Inherits the Steel</strong> &#8211; (translation) will premiere in January 2024!  Returning as Ryuuga Dogai is Wataru Kuriyama and returning as part of the directing team is veteran <strong>Garo</strong> director Yasuhiro Matsuda, alongside Yukazu Tanaka and Yoshikatsu Kimura.</p>
<p>Fans can visit the official site by <a href="https://t.co/sMvKe2mGNE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">clicking here</a>.</p>
<p>Stay tuned for more information on the return of <strong>Garo</strong>!</p>
